headline: Looking at the Changing Narrative for TTM Technologies After AI and Data Center Momentum
summary: TTM Technologies has seen a modest uptick in its fair value estimate to $77.50 from $76.00 as analysts grow more confident that AI driven demand and data center computing will support stronger long term fundamentals. Slightly higher revenue growth assumptions, now at about 8.11% from roughly 7.80%, are anchored in recent beat and raise quarters and expanding high end PCB capacity that should help capture incremental AI and high speed networking demand. Stay tuned to see how investors can...
